snippet: Justin Tucker hit a 52-yarder with 5 minutes 8 seconds left in overtime to give the Ravens a 23-20 road victory over the Steelers Thursday night.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Baltimore Ravens defeat Pittsburgh Steelers, 23-20, in overtime; other football news noted.
